OL,3,CSwinney to outline 100-day plan for
OL,4,CSNP government if re-elected
OL,6,FJohn Swinney will lay out a plan for
OL,7,Fthe first 100 days of a new SNP
OL,8,Fadministration on Monday, the party
OL,9,Fhas said.
OL,11,FIn a speech in Glasgow, the First
OL,12,FMinister is expected to pitch his
OL,13,Fparty as the only one with a "serious
OL,14,Fprogramme for government".
OL,26,@uD@^OUvD@YO]
