OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777246395
OL,3,CSwinney to outline 100-day plan for
OL,4,CSNP government if re-elected
OL,6,FThe SNP leader has already said he
OL,7,Fwould seek energy powers from
OL,8,FWestminster on the first day if he is
OL,9,Fsworn in again to the top job, as well
OL,10,Fas create a #10 million fund for
OL,11,Fbusinesses impacted by ferry
OL,12,Fdisruption.
OL,14,FThe party has also pledged to
OL,15,Flegislate for caps on food prices this
OL,16,Fyear, meaning work would likely have
OL,17,Fto begin early in a new SNP
OL,18,Fadministration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
