OL,3,CSwinney to outline 100-day plan for
OL,4,CSNP government if re-elected
OL,6,FSpeaking on Monday, the First Minister
OL,7,Fis expected to say: "During this
OL,8,Fcampaign, the SNP is the only party
OL,9,Fsetting out a serious programme for
OL,10,Fgovernment
OL,12,F"Every other party has spent the
OL,13,Fcampaign talking about themselves,
OL,14,Fabout each other and talking about the
OL,15,FSNP.
OL,17,F"But they never talk about you ` the
OL,18,Fpeople of Scotland.
OL,26,@oD@UOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
