OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777246395
OL,3,CSwinney to outline 100-day plan for
OL,4,CSNP government if re-elected
OL,6,F"They are asking you to vote for an
OL,7,Fopposition to stop things happening. I
OL,8,Fam asking you to vote for a SNP
OL,9,Fgovernment to get things done.
OL,11,F"The SNP want to lower your bills,
OL,12,Fother parties want to stop us.
OL,14,F"The SNP want to open GP walk-in
OL,15,Fclinics across Scotland. Other parties
OL,16,Fwant to stop us.
OL,18,F"The SNP want you to decide on your
OL,19,Ffuture. The other parties want to stop
OL,20,Fus.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
