OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777246395
OL,3,CSwinney to outline 100-day plan for
OL,4,CSNP government if re-elected
OL,6,F"The best way to ensure we can deliver
OL,7,Ffor you is by electing a majority SNP
OL,8,FGovernment."
OL,10,FHe will add: "A better Scotland is
OL,11,Fpossible. But we have to make it
OL,12,Fhappen. It is in your hands."
